<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Picking A Plan</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">What's a "connection"?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>A connection is one device streaming at a time. A 1-connection plan = one screen at a time. A 3-connection plan = three different people can watch different things simultaneously.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">Can I upgrade or change my plan later?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. You can upgrade to more connections or switch to a longer billing cycle at any time. Just contact support and we'll prorate the difference. Downgrades take effect at the next renewal.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">Does my subscription auto-renew?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes, plans renew automatically at the end of your billing cycle so service stays uninterrupted. You can cancel auto-renewal anytime from your Whop account dashboard — no cancellation fees, no questions asked.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">Which devices work with Just4us Media?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Firestick, Android TV, Android phones &amp; tablets, iOS (iPhone/iPad via compatible players), Smart TVs (Samsung, LG, Android TV built-in), MAG boxes, Enigma2, and any app that supports M3U or Xtream Codes. Setup guides are sent with your login credentials.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">What's the difference between Silver and Gold Partner?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Silver Partner ($250) gets you 25 reseller credits plus training and a private Telegram support group — perfect for launching a reseller business. Gold Partner ($750) includes 100 credits, priority white-label branding, revenue share eligibility, and quarterly strategy calls for partners who want to scale.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">How long does activation take?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Most accounts are activated within 5–60 minutes of purchase. In rare cases during high-volume periods, it may take up to 24 hours. You'll receive your login details by email as soon as activation is complete.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item open" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
        <div class="faq-q">Is there a free trial or refund?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>We offer a free 24-Hour All-Access Pass (no credit card required) so you can test the full service risk-free before committing. Subscription plans are non-refundable once activated — that's why we recommend starting with the free pass. See our <a href="https://www.just4usmedia.net/refund.html" style="color:var(--primary)">Refund Policy</a> for full details.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
